---
name: classify
description: Classifies text into one of the provided categories
model: claude-sonnet-4-6
provider: anthropic
temperature: 0.0
max_tokens: 64
vars:
  text: string
  categories: string
  allow_multiple: bool = false
---

Classify the following text into one of these categories: {{categories}}

{% if allow_multiple %}
You may return multiple categories if appropriate, as a comma-separated list.
{% endif %}

Return ONLY the category name(s). No explanation.

Text: {{text}}
